# 🎙️ Audio Folder Transcriber

A Python script that automatically converts and transcribes **multiple audio files from a folder** into a **single text transcript** using the [SpeechRecognition](https://pypi.org/project/SpeechRecognition/) and [pydub](https://pypi.org/project/pydub/) libraries.

---

## ✨ Features

- Supports multiple audio formats: `.mp3`, `.wav`, `.flac`, `.m4a`, `.aac`, `.ogg`, `.wma`
- Converts audio files to WAV format for compatibility
- Processes audio in chunks (default: 30 seconds) to handle long files
- Saves all transcriptions in one combined `.txt` file
- Easy to use via command-line

